- Use the App Router for better performance and organization of routes.
- Implement proper error boundaries to handle errors gracefully.
- Utilize Next.js's built-in image optimization features for faster loading times.
- Prefer static generation (SSG) over server-side rendering (SSR) when possible for improved performance.

